{"lemma":"رَدْمِ","slug":"رَدْمِ","root":"ر.د.م","root_slug":"ر-د-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-د-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"رَدْم","root":"ردم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15277","","n15280"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%92%D9%85%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cover with dust; to bury-over","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fill up (a hole in the ground)","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fill up (a hole in the ground); to backfill (a dug site, a trench, an excavation, and so on)","tags":["transitive"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ra.da.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15277","headword_ar":"رَدَمَ","root":"rdm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radomN","text_ar":"رَدْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, T, S, M, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stopped up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"closed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sad~a","text_ar":"سَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, T, S, M, Msb, K,) a door, (Lth, T, M, K,) or a place of entrance, (T,) and a gap, or breach, (Lth, T, S, M, Msb, K,) and the like, (Lth, T, M, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wholly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the extent of a third thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or it signifies more than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sad~a","text_ar":"سَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he stopped up by putting one thing upon another;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in building up a doorway or the like;] for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~adomu","text_ar":"الرَّدْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is “ that of which one part is put upon another. ” (M.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radama","text_ar":"رَدَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radomN","text_ar":"رَدْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rd~m","text_ar":"ردّم","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarodiymN","text_ar":"تَرْدِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trd~m","text_ar":"تردّم","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He patched,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a garment, or piece of cloth; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"patched,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in several places."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rudima","text_ar":"رُدِمَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(anything)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was put, and joined,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sewed, one part to another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radama Alqawosa","text_ar":"رَدَمَ القَوْسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radomN","text_ar":"رَدْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He caused the bow to make a sound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to twang,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by pulling the string and then letting it go."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K. *) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rudimati Alqawosu","text_ar":"رُدِمَتِ القَوْسُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The bow was so caused to make a sound."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radama","text_ar":"رَدَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarodimu","text_ar":"يَرْدِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarodumu","text_ar":"يَرْدُمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, (accord. to different copies of the S, [in one copy"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raduma","text_ar":"رَدُمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, which is a mistake,]) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rudaAmN","text_ar":"رُدَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K; *) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radama","text_ar":"رَدَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a camel, and of an ass, aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarodimu","text_ar":"يَرْدِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radomN","text_ar":"رَدْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K, *) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rudaAmN","text_ar":"رُدَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the subst.; or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radama bihaA","text_ar":"رَدَمَ بِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radomN","text_ar":"رَدْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", used in a general manner; (M;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke wind, with a sound."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K. *)       -A4-  See also 4, in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","Lth","T","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n15280","headword_ar":"رَدْمٌ","root":"rdm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is an inf. n. and also a subst. [in the proper sense of this term]: (S, M, TA:) as the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sad~N","text_ar":"سَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K *) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sud~N","text_ar":"سُدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M) [as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing intervening between two other things, preventing the passage from one to the other; an obstruction; a barrier; any building with which a place is obstructed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; a meaning erroneously assigned in the B to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radamN","text_ar":"رَدَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing of which one part is put upon another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rampart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fortified barrier:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"larger than a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sd~","text_ar":"سدّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and is [said to be] from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vawobN murad~amN","text_ar":"ثَوْبٌ مُرَدَّمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning “ [a garment, or piece of cloth,] having patches upon patches: ” (Bd in xviii. 94:) and signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything having parts put, and joined"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sewed, one upon another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruduwmN","text_ar":"رُدُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~adomu","text_ar":"الرَّدْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies particularly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The rampart"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~ud~u","text_ar":"السُّدُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", M, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~ad~u","text_ar":"السَّدُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is between us"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the people of the territory of the Muslims"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and Yájooj and Májooj"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Gog and Magog"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, K, * TA:) mentioned in the Kur xviii. 94. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What falls,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and lies in a heap, one part upon another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a wall in a state of demolition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a general sense:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or particularly the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twang"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a bow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An emission of wind from the anus, with a sound;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rudaAmN","text_ar":"رُدَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or this is a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radama","text_ar":"رَدَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a camel, and of an ass, meaning “ he broke wind with a sound. ” (M.) ―         -b3-  And, applied to a man, (M,) (assumed tropical:)  One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in whom is no good;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rudaAmN","text_ar":"رُدَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mirodaAmN","text_ar":"مِرْدَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","TA","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}